!power {{
	--name|Tentacle Rod

	--To Hit 1| [[ 1d20 + 9 ]]
	--To Hit 2| [[ 1d20 + 9 ]]
	--To Hit 3| [[ 1d20 + 9 ]]
	--Reach| 15 ft.
	--Damage 1| [[ 1d6 ]] Bludgeoning
	--Damage 2| [[ 1d6 ]] Bludgeoning
	--Damage 3| [[ 1d6 ]] Bludgeoning
	--Saving Throw| 15 Con Save
	--Effect| If all 3 tentacles hit 1 creature: the creature's speed is halved, it has disadvantage on Dexterity saving throws, and it can't use reactions. Moreover, on each of its turns, it can take either an action or a bonus action, but not both. At the end of each of its turns, it can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success.
	--Duration| 1 minute
}}